      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained interior\u2014reflects an uncompromising standard of care. Mechanically sound and aesthetically pristine, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. This is an investment-grade example intended for those who demand excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
